Detailed Description

template<typename PTYPE>
class muscle::ConduitEntranceArray< PTYPE >

complementary class for the Java muscle.core.JNIConduitEntrance using primitive type arrays, e.g.

muscle.core.JNIConduitEntrance<double[], Object>
use muscle::ConduitEntranceSingle to access single primitive data instead of arrays access an entrance which yields arrays (send)

Jan Hegewald
